&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html">New maple leaves in the garden at Myoshinji/Taizo-in temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07883.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2204_A7R07883.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Looking West・西を向いて</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220423/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Looking West・西を向いて" /><published>2022-04-23T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-04-23T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/looking</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220423/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
